575
00:43:25,003 --> 00:43:26,129
Está bem.

576
00:43:27,239 --> 00:43:28,433
você está linda.

577
00:43:44,556 --> 00:43:45,716
Desculpe, maninha.

578
00:43:46,892 --> 00:43:48,154
Perdi o apetite.

579
00:43:55,166 --> 00:43:56,497
